<div itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Product">
<h1>Welcome to Executive Auto Group  Hartford New and Used Car Dealer</h1>
<p>Thank you for visiting Executive Auto Group. Since 1981 we have served the Hartford, New Haven, and Meriden areas and have helped new car and used car buyers find the perfect vehicles to drive home in. After decades of service to our customers, we have become synonymous with providing a quality selection, excellent prices, and friendly service.</p> 
<p>The honest and courteous staff at each of the Executive Auto Group dealers understands the needs of each customer, and look forward to providing not only the vehicle that will fit your needs, but also the prices you want. Among the range of quality brands we offer include Acura, Honda, Jeep, Dodge, KIA, Nissan, and Mazda not to mention the full gamut of pre-owned vehicles. In other words, the Executive Auto Group has exactly what youre looking for! </p>
<strong>New and Used Auto Dealership Serving:</strong><br>
<ul style="list-style-type:none;">
<li>Hartford, CT</li>
<li>New Britain, CT</li>
